<br>
I am not the main damage dealer here.<br>
I can hold aggro fine with only one weapon. This weapon in my off hand is just a timy bit of overkill.<br>
Why not use my shield?<br>
<br>
I started using the shield for PB groups because of this, and have never looked back.<br>
<br>
Sometimes I will not use it in this manner, if someone else has higher shield skill.<br>
<br>
If I am one of the main damage dealers (IE: main tank or all melee group), I need that extra damage from the off-hand weapon. Though on occasion I will still use the shield if the &quot;main tank&quot; is higher season than I am and uses LW or spear. In these cases, using the off hand weapon often ends up with me as the main tank, even though that was not the plan (even if the main is 2 or 3 seasons above me, is taunting, and I am not taunting.) Because of this I will use the shield to limit my damage output (now I will not be the main tank at all), and the main tank now has a little added protection.<br>
